#

Crispy Fried Chicken

50 min
$12.99
400 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten

Cuisine:

Description

Juicy chicken with a crunchy, golden crust that’s perfect for any meal!

Ingredients

  • chicken pieces (legs, thighs, breasts): 2 lbs
  • buttermilk: 2 cups
  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • salt: 2 tsp
  • black pepper: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
  • vegetable oil: for frying
